Sakai, 1971
</taxonomicName>
, off southwestern Taiwan: 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[848,860,1756,1777]" pageId="1" pageNumber="174">a</emphasis>
, stn CST 2, 1360–1669 m, ovigerous female (cl 163.5 mm, pcl 110.9 mm, cw 100.5 mm), NTOU A01420; 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[621,634,1786,1807]" pageId="1" pageNumber="174">b</emphasis>
, stn PCP445, 982–999 m, male (cl 34.0 mm, pcl 22.0 mm, cw 20.0 mm), NTOU A01419; 
